{"tid":2077004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《南華早報》：中国駐港安全機關會緝拿美國在港間諜","createTime":"2020-06-24T03:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T13:55:12.000Z","uid":892,"like":161,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"ef027dd4875de4cc20f2776ba1589f9f6b3f346e","tid":2077004,"uid":892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/weatherjj/26904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fweatherjj%2F26904&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPnWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=bb6fc2c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/weatherjj/26904</a><br />\n<br />\n《南華早報》報導，中国官員昨日會見逾百名親中派人士，收集他們對港區国安法的支持和意見。<br />\n<br />\n席間有中国官員透露，中国駐港安全機關的管轄權會用於緝拿美國在港間諜，而管轄權非常廣泛，包括執法和審訊。<br />\n<br />\n報導亦指出，昨日會面為中国政府就港區国安法的最後一次「公開諮詢」。<br />\n<br />\n相關報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3090292/top-chinese-officials-hear-views-national-security-law\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F3090292%2Ftop-chinese-officials-hear-views-national-security-law&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPnWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=07d62b4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3090292/top-chinese-officials-hear-views-national-security-law</a><br />\n<br />\n#香港政治"},{"pid":"f5bb6b018669e3d5a6c008b1c3552e3dd1caf2b0","tid":2077004,"uid":20362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T03:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c310e9fbbe07c82c43d16b1f3bddc2aa72c3d39","tid":2077004,"uid":55089,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T03:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj