":"<strong></strong>China conducting covert biological weapons research, State Department says<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2020/jun/23/china-conducting-covert-biological-weapons-researc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtontimes.com%2Fnews%2F2020%2Fjun%2F23%2Fchina-conducting-covert-biological-weapons-researc%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPnWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=9616625d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2020/jun/23/china-conducting-covert-biological-weapons-researc/</a><br />\n美國國務院週二公佈的一份報告稱，中國正在開展與秘密生物武器有關的研究，並且沒有透露過去進攻性生化武器的工作。<br />\n<br />\n中國一直都在做生化武器研發！<br />\n<br />\n年度軍備控制遵從報告稱，北京還通過封鎖用於探測地下核爆炸的國際監測系統中的傳感器來隱藏與核有關的測試數據。<br />\n 這份未分類的報告提供了有關美國「多年」關注北京生物武器研究的新細節，這是包括中國和美國在內的183個國家簽署的1972年《生物武器公約》所不允許的。"},{"pid":"86170dccd358523aff11b9a204ba9cc3c8e72536","tid":2077004,"uid":117509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c305c96160e9ed6df940721f63f48cedbf497b82","tid":2077004,"uid":66087,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T03:29:48.000Z","msg":"中共已經完全唔怕美國佬...<br />\n<br />\n話知你香港死，佢地唔在乎<br />\n<br />\n完全係最差既情況 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T03:55:51.000Z","msg":"最差唔係中共唔怕美國而瘋狂打壓香港人<br />\n而係咁做之餘完全冇人伸出援手同制裁<br />\n<br />\n當美國話之你香港死唔在乎時<br />\n就算點都好一定要走，到時真真正正冇得救<br />\n因為有能力既香港人不論黃藍都雞飛狗走<br />\n呢個先係最差既情況"},{"pid":"89214eeb04e71de8cc4e7df7cd77475dc5f47385","tid":2077004,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T04:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DQh1D9M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDQh1D9M.jpg&h=b956aa83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b245aa140a2cfd7ca7c5acb632d683e26a70acd","tid":2077004,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T04:02:53.000Z","msg":"邵善波會唔會仆街"},{"pid":"590c1b92f6af21bd215b6178e77fea658e761143","tid"